{"tid":1945272,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"特朗普正式簽署「台灣法案」  強化正式外交關係","createTime":"2020-03-27T02:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T06:35:01.000Z","uid":227801,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"eb2e7f93ca34f6a43ee713f1f2e490fcd550c238","tid":1945272,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:52:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1276739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1276739&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNi3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=0b066351\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1276739</a><br />\n特朗普正式簽署「台灣法案」<br />\n27.03.2020 09:54<br />\n美國總統特朗普正式簽署「台灣法案」，是繼「台灣旅行法」後，另一個以台灣命名的美國法律。「台灣法案」要求美國行政部門支持台灣強化正式外交關係，貿易代表署亦應與美國國會協商，尋求增進美台雙邊經貿關係。在國際參與方面，法案要求華府在適當情況下，支持台灣在所有並非以主權國家為參與資格的國際組織，成為會員，並在其他適當組織中，取得觀察員身份。法案又呼籲華府對於台灣造成傷害的國家，應該考慮改變與有關國家的經濟、安全及外交接觸。"},{"pid":"dd29f804ced3a80260f1c944aa829401fdfd6c98","tid":1945272,"uid":325840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:53:57.000Z","msg":"今日有4位至少還押80日手足會上庭，跪求聲援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1944875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1944875</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d6067f1fec3774f07b5f9a0499e503c4b5a9e2bc","tid":1945272,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdda3afb448af18acbd0454485bad96fc4bd4121","tid":1945272,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e5e8e9aa54bcada7cdc4ff1098bdda0072d78d","tid":1945272,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:02:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f3e7bc8449b6d36b0f932286935574631b693f4c","tid":194